metadata.name: Automorphosis II
metadata.description:
Automorphosis II by JVDE / Janus van den Eijnden

A surrealistic exploration of the intersection between technology and humanity. Created for the AI Surrealism exhibition with Superchief Gallery NFT NY and Exquisite Workers, the largest AI art show in history, 2023. Curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.

PNG 5376 x 3580 . JVDE 2023
